  "notes": [
    "Status remains incomplete until a native-WebGPU v2 evidence bundle is captured on the current adapter.",
    "The live material consumes the patch-resident storage atlas and its first patch-local mip; gutters derive from declared warp/filter/derivative/projected-footprint support and dirty updates are patch-indexed.",
    "The runtime selects a six-face horizon-aware frontier from physical-pixel projected error, globally enforces 2:1 balance, submits one indexed group per leaf, and morphs transition edges to the exact next-coarser bilinear representation.",
    "Planet/atmosphere integration publishes metric radii, body/world transforms, ECEF conversion, altitude, and world-up queries from one worldUnitsPerMeter contract.",
    "The fused height derivative is candidate-only and does not drive the preview normal; derivative correctness remains unproved.",
    "The default scene MRT is output-only; no normal or velocity attachment is allocated without a consumer."
  ]
